 \"his volleyball career\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"12 months\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"a four-year sentence\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His inclusion has been one of the biggest talking points heading into thissummer's Gameswith Dutch officials standing by their decision to select him.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 673, \"end\": 678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_people\", \"score\": 0.6869586773773817, \"rank\": 0.23890701985321505, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His inclusion\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest talking points\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"their decision\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Radcliffe, a former world champion marathon runner who represented Great Britain in four consecutive Olympic Games between 1996 and 2008, told LBC van de Velde 'may well have turned his life around' following his conviction, wishing him 'the best of luck'.\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.6521038325961866, \"rank\": 0.5334957315531297, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999968006437732, \"rank\": 2.873718609405132e-06, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 875, \"end\": 878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999962751644, \"rank\": 3.724739348922391e-09, \"text\": \"LBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a former world champion marathon runner\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"four consecutive Olympic Games\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"his conviction\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"luck\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think that is a very dangerous line to go down given that we allow people who cheat in sport and take drugs in sport to then come back and then compete,' Radcliffe told Tonight with Andrew Marr.\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.6521038325961866, \"rank\": 0.5334957315531297, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Marr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Marr\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Marr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Marr\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very dangerous line\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"drugs\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"Tonight\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So, to ban someone, as I understand it, he was 19 at the time and he's served his jail time and it's a long time to carry on paying for that mistake for the rest of your life.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1365, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1251}, {\"ngram\": \"his jail time\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"that mistake\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He may well have turned it around and completely repented.\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You certainly hope, I know that he is married now and has settled down.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think it's a tough thing to do to punish him twice and if he's managed to successfully turn his life around after being sent to prison and to qualify and to be playing sport at the highest level, then I actually wish him the best of luck.\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tough thing\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"prison\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest level\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"luck\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Obviously, he will be watched during the village, if it were to be repeated now or it had been last year I would be saying a different thing.\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1792}, {\"ngram\": \"a different thing\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I think the ban and the learning difference from 19 to 29 is huge.'\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ban\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"the learning difference\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Radcliffe's comments were widely criticised on social media, with one X user describing them as 'shocking'.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.6521038325961866, \"rank\": 0.5334957315531297, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"one X user\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I really apologise for the way I phrased this.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The utter condemnation of the crime in my head went without saying but I should have clarified that.\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The utter condemnation\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"the crime\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead I poorly jumped to explaining why It would be great to exclude all who betray ideals but legally not possible.\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2337, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ideals\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Responding to the post, Radcliffe said: 'I agree and can only apologise, that is not what I intended to say.\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2363, \"end\": 2372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.6521038325961866, \"rank\": 0.5334957315531297, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the post\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I stress that it is not something that can be excused in any way.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"any way\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was confused in my head and responding to the right to ban him from the Games and I do not know why I wished him luck.\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2569}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Again I apologise.\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not support him taking part, I was confused because I was clumsily trying to say that he can not be banned, he has served his jail time.\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2690}, {\"ngram\": \"his jail time\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Ideally it would be great ban athletes that do not uphold the Olympic ideals and general human standards but legally that can not happen.\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2939, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great ban athletes\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic ideals\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2878}, {\"ngram\": \"general human standards\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Again, I fully apologise, I do not wish him luck in any way and do not know why I said that phrase at the end.\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 3052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"luck\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 2990}, {\"ngram\": \"any way\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3001}, {\"ngram\": \"that phrase\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3040}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't my intention.'\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my intention\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Netherlands team boss Pieter van den Hoogenband explained this week 'measures' have been taken to facilitate Van de Velde's participation at the Games.\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3079, \"end\": 3090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9984649274180676, \"rank\": 0.0015371116741091041, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3101, \"end\": 3126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pieter_van_den_Hoogenband\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pieter van den Hoogenband\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pieter_van_den_Hoogenband\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pieter_van_den_Hoogenband\"}, {\"begin\": 3101, \"end\": 3126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pieter_van_den_Hoogenband\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pieter van den Hoogenband\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pieter_van_den_Hoogenband\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pieter_van_den_Hoogenband\"}], \"noun_phrase